1. *Priznao* je da ne zna odgovor. (He admitted he didn't know the answer.)
2. On je *priznao* da je pogre≈°io. (He admitted he was wrong.)
3. Ona je *priznala* da nije zadovoljna. (She admitted she wasn't satisfied.)
